{"data":[{"name":"88:1","price":"(1) Has there reached you the report of the Overwhelming [event]?","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡغَٰشِيَةِ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5968,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:2","price":"(2) [Some] faces, that Day, will be humbled,","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ خَٰشِعَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5969,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:3","price":"(3) Working [hard] and exhausted.[1910]","arabic":"عَامِلَةٞ نَّاصِبَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5970,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1910]- Another accepted meaning is \"They were working hard and exhausted,\" i.e., doing deeds during worldly life which did not benefit them since they were not accompanied by faith or done for the acceptance of Allāh (subḥānahu wa taʿālā) .","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:4","price":"(4) They will [enter to] burn in an intensely hot Fire.","arabic":"تَصۡلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5971,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:5","price":"(5) They will be given drink from a boiling spring.","arabic":"تُسۡقَىٰ مِنۡ عَيۡنٍ ءَانِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5972,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:6","price":"(6) For them there will be no food except from a poisonous, thorny plant","arabic":"لَّيۡسَ لَهُمۡ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5973,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:7","price":"(7) Which neither nourishes nor avails against hunger.","arabic":"لَّا يُسۡمِنُ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِن جُوعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5974,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:8","price":"(8) [Other] faces, that Day, will show pleasure.","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاعِمَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5975,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:9","price":"(9) With their effort [they are] satisfied","arabic":"لِّسَعۡيِهَا رَاضِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5976,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:10","price":"(10) In an elevated garden,","arabic":"فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5977,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:11","price":"(11) Wherein they will hear no unsuitable speech.[1911]","arabic":"لَّا تَسۡمَعُ فِيهَا لَٰغِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5978,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1911]- i.e., any insult, falsehood, immorality, idle or vain talk, etc.","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:12","price":"(12) Within it is a flowing spring.","arabic":"فِيهَا عَيۡنٞ جَارِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5979,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:13","price":"(13) Within it are couches raised high","arabic":"فِيهَا سُرُرٞ مَّرۡفُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5980,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:14","price":"(14) And cups put in place","arabic":"وَأَكۡوَابٞ مَّوۡضُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5981,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:15","price":"(15) And cushions lined up","arabic":"وَنَمَارِقُ مَصۡفُوفَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5982,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:16","price":"(16) And carpets spread around.","arabic":"وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبۡثُوثَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5983,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:17","price":"(17) Then do they not look at the camels - how they are created?","arabic":"أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡإِبِلِ كَيۡفَ خُلِقَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5984,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:18","price":"(18) And at the sky - how it is raised?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5985,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:19","price":"(19) And at the mountains - how they are erected?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5986,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:20","price":"(20) And at the earth - how it is spread out?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَيۡفَ سُطِحَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5987,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:21","price":"(21) So remind, [O Muḥammad]; you are only a reminder.","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5988,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:22","price":"(22) You are not over them a controller.","arabic":"لَّسۡتَ عَلَيۡهِم بِمُصَيۡطِرٍ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5989,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:23","price":"(23) However, he who turns away and disbelieves –","arabic":"إِلَّا مَن تَوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5990,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:24","price":"(24) Then Allāh will punish him with the greatest punishment.","arabic":"فَيُعَذِّبُهُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلۡعَذَابَ ٱلۡأَكۡبَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5991,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:25","price":"(25) Indeed, to Us is their return.","arabic":"إِنَّ إِلَيۡنَآ إِيَابَهُمۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5992,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"88:26","price":"(26) Then indeed, upon Us is their account.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا حِسَابَهُم","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5993,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah","Chapter Al-Ghashiyah","Ghashiyah","Surah Ghashiyah","Chapter Ghashiyah","Al Ghashiyah","Surah Al Ghashiyah","Chapter Al Ghashiyah","Surah 88","Chapter 88","The Overwhelming Event","الغاشية"]}